message.body: Hey mom can you text me a picture of the invite for Katie's shower next week?
￼Questions? Hope you're having a nice relaxing weekend!
Thanks! Just trying to figure out where I should be when
I think dad & I aren't leaving here till sat am so we won't get there much before the shower anyway. Call tomorrow when you have time.
￼Sideshow bob spent the night outside & got rained on....seems happy though!
